  "2386340": {
    "name": "水族馆物语: 人鱼世界",
    "steam_appid": 2386340,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386340/extras/4192c59fba9452f33afa7b6024797b25.avif?t=1756499782\" alt=\"星座美人鱼\" width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>打造梦想水族馆，养鱼养成美人鱼！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《水族馆物语》是一款融合经营模拟与收集养成的水族馆游戏。你将成为一名馆长，饲养超过百种超萌美人鱼与奇幻海洋生物！还能自由建设水族馆，从珊瑚礁到外太空，数百款主题装饰任你随心搭配，打造专属於你的梦幻海洋王国！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更可挑战益智小游戏，获得丰富奖励。透过资源管理、制作纪念商品，并与其他玩家自由交易，建立属于你的海洋事业！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386340/extras/c50f0947051213d8ebc5b815add556e4.poster.avif?t=1756499782\" aria-label=\"梦想水族馆\" width=614 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386340/extras/c50f0947051213d8ebc5b815add556e4.webm?t=1756499782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386340/extras/c50f0947051213d8ebc5b815add556e4.mp4?t=1756499782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>养鱼收藏，享受治愈时光</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验最chill的养鱼收藏乐趣！看着超可爱的海洋生物在你的水族馆里悠哉游泳，从萌萌的小丑鱼到神秘的海盗灯笼鱼，应有尽有。每条鱼都有自己的性格和魅力，营造完美的治愈氛围，让你瞬间放松！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386340/extras/58937141434c989eaa42a55776e45145.poster.avif?t=1756499782\" aria-label=\"疗癒养鱼\" width=614 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386340/extras/58937141434c989eaa42a55776e45145.webm?t=1756499782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386340/extras/58937141434c989eaa42a55776e45145.mp4?t=1756499782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>见证小鱼进化成传说美人鱼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亲眼目睹普通鱼类华丽变身成传说美人鱼的神奇瞬间！通过精心照料和特殊培养，看着你的水中小伙伴经历超震撼的进化蜕变。超多独特美人鱼品种，每一种都有专属的绝美造型和特殊技能，简直不要太棒！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386340/extras/58c660f1c79a09d8f68415777a394cec.poster.avif?t=1756499782\" aria-label=\"人鱼进化\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386340/extras/58c660f1c79a09d8f68415777a394cec.webm?t=1756499782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386340/extras/58c660f1c79a09d8f68415777a394cec.mp4?t=1756499782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自由设计专属鱼你的水族乐园</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随心所欲设计水族馆的每个角落！从数百种装饰中挑选你的最爱 - 椰子树、珊瑚礁、展示架还有各种主题装饰。为不同生物打造专属地盘，建设游客参观路线，创造属于你个人style的完美水族世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386340/extras/247bd6cd8ea29aa2e6d4dfaa0d3f027f.poster.avif?t=1756499782\" aria-label=\"自由建筑\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386340/extras/247bd6cd8ea29aa2e6d4dfaa0d3f027f.webm?t=1756499782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386340/extras/247bd6cd8ea29aa2e6d4dfaa0d3f027f.mp4?t=1756499782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>策略经营・成为水族大亨</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运营超成功的水族馆生意！收集原材料，开发游客周边产品，合理管理各种资源。平衡鱼类养护、装修预算和纪念品制作，建造全世界最赚钱的水族馆帝国，成为真正的水族馆大亨！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386340/extras/c0d34a3a10741f56fd1a988c0e771cdf.poster.avif?t=1756499782\" aria-label=\"商品生产\" width=614 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386340/extras/c0d34a3a10741f56fd1a988c0e771cdf.webm?t=1756499782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386340/extras/c0d34a3a10741f56fd1a988c0e771cdf.mp4?t=1756499782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>※ 游戏特色：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >► 收集饲养上百种美人鱼与海洋生物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >► 养鱼进化，解锁隐藏美人鱼造型</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >► 多元经营模拟，资源放置产出，游客任务挑战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >► 合成特色纪念品，交易稀有道具</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >► 三消与合成小游戏，多元玩法乐趣</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >► 上百种主题装饰，自由打造你的专属空间</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >► 与好友协力，衝刺全球排行榜</p>",
